			<m:mrow>
				<m:mi> B </m:mi>
			</m:mrow>
		</m:msub>
	</m:math>
. Then, we reverse the direction of reference velocity 
<m:math>
		<m:msub>
			<m:mi mathvariant="bold"> v </m:mi>
			<m:mrow>
				<m:mi> B </m:mi>
			</m:mrow>
		</m:msub>
	</m:math>
and find the resultant relative velocity, 
<m:math>
